instruction: Research and compile state-level residential emission data for the past five years.
output: Based on the increasing interest of investors in state-level residential emission data, I have conducted a thorough research and compiled the necessary data for the past five years. This data will help us understand the level of emissions in each state and the initiatives that have been introduced to lower these emissions. With this information, we can make informed investment decisions and support state-level initiatives that aim to reduce residential emissions.
